{"tid":2303831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局拒停課 毒襲大中小學","createTime":"2020-11-28T09:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T10:21:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4f584c43224541ba4d91dd05b7b24eaaec2d56","tid":2303831,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/HFBLYIZYBVBFVKB35GU5U4T5TI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FHFBLYIZYBVBFVKB35GU5U4T5TI%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Ck6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=969e1eee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FHFBLYIZYBVBFVKB35GU5U4T5TI%2F&h=4631123e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/HFBLYIZYBVBFVKB35GU5U4T5TI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n教育局拒停課 毒襲大中小學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JNmh9-_U9Kk8ICWOGpLlk7SnRD0=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JP6MPQLJFVB3JHAXAE2SVTTI5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJNmh9-_U9Kk8ICWOGpLlk7SnRD0%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJP6MPQLJFVB3JHAXAE2SVTTI5M.jpg&h=066273ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聖保羅男女中學暫停面授課，學生須取樽檢測。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】第四波疫潮不斷蔓延，全港多間學校近日陸續出現感染個案，教育局仍拒絕宣佈全港停課。昨日再多三名學生染疫，旺角聖公會諸聖中學一名14歲學生確診，需停課14天；啟晴邨何壽南小學有學生初步確診，其家長亦已確診；教育大學亦有一名學生確診。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：養和爆疫 病人亡 醫護中招  全院3,200員工檢測 33樓封閉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諸聖男生確診 全校檢測<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心昨公佈，聖公會諸聖中學一名14歲男生確診，他11月24日發病，翌日求醫及交樣本後確診，最近一次上學是11月26日，上學期間師生都有戴口罩，沒有密切接觸者，但學校須停課14日，全校師生要檢測。男生11月26日亦曾到長沙灣一間補習社補習，同場數名學生及教師有戴口罩，中心會視乎情況安排檢疫或派樣本樽。據了解，男生就讀中四的哥哥及曾與他一起用膳的同學要家居隔離。<br />\n<br />\n位於啟晴邨的何壽南小學。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：罷工醫護扣薪 留人事紀錄  恐影響升遷 工會轟醫管局秋後算賬<br />\n<br />\n據了解，聖保羅男女中學一名英文老師被列作密切接觸者，已請病假數日，由於。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港教育大學一名文化與創意藝術學系的學生確診，其最後上學日為11月23日，大學已經聯絡與該名學生有密切接觸的人，相。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"b0d601c15ad4fb5d8f5651ae96f6f34c57582f22","tid":2303831,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>政治凌駕健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"02aca9d50a44537c740238f9d3ebe9736f5c75aa","tid":2303831,"uid":118520,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"b0d601c15ad4fb5d8f5651ae96f6f34c57582f22","tid":2303831,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>政治凌駕健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"你都on9  後生仔抵抗力強 根本無需要停課"},{"pid":"57ed3fb988cf1bab4c28dee7f3a052a55b0efc3b","tid":2303831,"uid":357031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"通過咗国安法，市民安居樂業，無須停課 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823241309c021a626b41b40cc557269da4211d36","tid":2303831,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"十二月四日有大function"},{"pid":"b3c6532a68623fe761385cd4da9c2d42686c4fde","tid":2303831,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"牙侵七十鳩幾歲中完幾日就好返仲可以去選總統，香港班十鳩幾歲唔想返學就呱呱叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd44e04be30e6e66c95f4fe2ecdd11042cbe567","tid":2303831,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02aca9d50a44537c740238f9d3ebe9736f5c75aa","tid":2303831,"uid":118520,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"b0d601c15ad4fb5d8f5651ae96f6f34c57582f22","tid":2303831,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":